data.value:
If you need help or have any questions, please send me an email to maud.picq.13@ucl.ac.uk
The status bar displays the current state of the tool: - "recording initial data" - "experimenting": during this phase, you will receive a notification of the amount of time you have wasted every 5 minutes - "analyzing data": the data analysis is run directly on your computer - "report generated": the experiment is now finished; please click on the link to fill a quick survey, and then send the report (named Report_UserProductivity.txt, and located on your desktop) by email to maud.picq.13@ucl.ac.uk
